{
  "stem": "24625.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They never had an apple because we eat them before they grew out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We used to steal the apples and eat them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The carrots, they never could hide them far enough for us because we used to dig out all the carrots in the fields and eat the carrots.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Beets-- we used to go in the fields from the peasants and pull out all the beets.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were always complaining.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A just reason, because we were eating them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this was meant for the cows, not for the people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we were as hungry as the cows, so we were eating it too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But the children, they wanted to eat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We used to eat two slices of bread a day, I remember, for breakfast.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And bread-- black bread, you could take it and throw it against the wall, and it would stick against the wall.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So bad, it was because they didn't have anything else.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And mainly we eat cabbage because they had a lot of cabbage and herring because there was a lot of herring during the war in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Everybody was cooking herring.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "All kind-- I can tell you 10 different ways how to make herring.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My mama, I remember, made gefilte fish with herring.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Don't ask how it tastes, you know, but at that time, that's what we were eating.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And fried herring, and cooked herring, and baked herring.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And when I came back from the, the camp, I couldn't look at a cabbage for, I think, five years in a row because that's all we had, every day, every day, every day cabbage, cabbage, cabbage, and herring.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This was really something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's the way it went.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Definitely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Definitely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was very lucky because I ran extremely fast.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They couldn't catch me.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
